                    <chunk name="param_input" index="1">
                      <items count="6">
                        <item name="Description" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">The robot system will select the orientation type (ABB = quaternions, KUKA = Euler angles in degrees, UR = axis angles in radians). If this input is left unconnected, it will assume the 3D rotation is expressed in quaternions.</item>
